high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter left of the sink.
Pick up the knife that is near the apple.
Turn right, move to the black counter left of the microwave.
Slice the apple, let pieces fall on the floor.
Turn right, move to the black counter in front of the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn left, move to the black counter left of the microwave.
Pick up a section of apple.
Turn right, move to the black counter in front of the microwave.
Put the apple section in the microwave, cook it, pick it back up.
Turn left, move to the black counter left of the microwave.
Put the apple section on to the black counter left of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Cook an apple section and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left to go to the front of the sink.
Pick up the yellow knife on the right of the red tomato.
Turn around and go to the small black table on the right of the refrigerator.
Cut the apple on the table. into three parts.
Move right to the front of the microwave on top of the black table.
Place the knife inside the microwave.
Move left back to the cut apple.
Pick up one piece of apple on the table.
Move over right to the microwave.
Microwave the cut apple piece behind the knife, and take the apple out.
Move to the left side of the black table.
Place the apple back on the top of the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved apple piece on table.

high_descs: Go to the left of the sink
Take the knife from the drying rack
Go to the microwave table
Cut the apple on the table
Go to the microwave
Put the knife in the microwave
Go to the apple
Pick up a slice of apple
Go to the microwave
Heat the slice of apple
Take the apple out and look at the plates
Put the apple on the left plate
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked slice of apple on a plate
